indoor play areas, professional pet care experts, offering pet care. Their...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/barking-hound-village-inn-atlanta\",\"name\":\"Barking Hound Village Inn\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/barking-hound-village-inn-atlanta\",\"description\":\"Barking Hound Village Inn is a premier dog boarding and daycare facility in Atlanta. This facility features spacious indoor and outdoor play areas, professional grooming stations, and certified pet...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dunwoody-village-ace-hardware\",\"name\":\"Dunwoody Village Ace Hardware\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dunwoody-village-ace-hardware\",\"description\":\"Dog lovers in Atlanta trust Dunwoody Village Ace Hardware for exceptional care. This facility features spacious exercise zones, trained pet care specialists, offering pet care. Their services...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wag-a-lot-downtown-atlanta\",\"name\":\"WAG-A-LOT Downtown\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wag-a-lot-downtown-atlanta\",\"description\":\"Dog lovers in Atlanta trust WAG-A-LOT Downtown for exceptional care. This facility features professional grooming stations, passionate pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wagging-tails-doggie-daycare-boarding-atlanta\",\"name\":\"Wagging Tails Doggie Daycare & Boarding\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wagging-tails-doggie-daycare-boarding-atlanta\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in Atlanta consistently rave about Wagging Tails Doggie Daycare & Boarding. This facility features spacious exercise zones, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I walk my dog indoors in Atlanta?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Not yet in our verified directory for Atlanta. If you know a great indoor option, you can submit it and we’ll review it for inclusion.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in the City of Atlanta?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Atlanta strictly enforces leash laws in all public spaces. Dogs must be on a leash at all times unless they are within the fenced boundaries of a designated off-leash dog park. Owners must also maintain control of their pets and are legally required to remove any waste immediately.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed in Piedmont Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Piedmont Park is extremely dog-friendly. It features the Piedmont Park Dog Park, a premier off-leash area with separate enclosures for large and small breeds. Outside of this area, dogs are welcome on leashes throughout the park's many scenic paths and meadows.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the requirements for Atlanta dog parks?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Dogs must be at least four months old, current on rabies vaccinations, and wearing visible tags. Prong, pinch, or spiked collars are typically prohibited within the off-leash zones to ensure a safe play environment for all canine visitors.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Atlanta\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San