ity-hero-copy\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-breadcrumbs\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Home\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Atlanta\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-eyebrow\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"City spotlight\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Indoor Dog Park in Atlanta, GA\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Experience the urban energy of Atlanta, featuring the iconic Piedmont Park and a thriving community of dog-friendly businesses and green spaces.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Atlanta, Georgia, is a premier destination for dog owners who value a blend of urban excitement and lush green spaces. The city's pet culture is anchored by the iconic \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.piedmontpark.org\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Piedmont Park\\\"}],null,\\\", which provides a massive off-leash area and miles of scenic trails with skyline views. Neighborhoods like the Old Fourth Ward and Inman Park offer easy access to the \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.beltline.org\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Atlanta BeltLine\\\"}],null,\\\", a mult