 and certified pet...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dunwoody-village-ace-hardware\",\"name\":\"Dunwoody Village Ace Hardware\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dunwoody-village-ace-hardware\",\"description\":\"Dog lovers in Atlanta trust Dunwoody Village Ace Hardware for exceptional care. This facility features spacious exercise zones, trained pet care specialists, offering pet care. Their services...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wag-a-lot-downtown-atlanta\",\"name\":\"WAG-A-LOT Downtown\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wag-a-lot-downtown-atlanta\",\"description\":\"Dog lovers in Atlanta trust WAG-A-LOT Downtown for exceptional care. This facility features professional grooming stations, passionate pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wagging-tails-doggie-daycare-boarding-atlanta\",\"name\":\"Wagging Tails Doggie Daycare & Boarding\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/wagging-tails-doggie-daycare-boarding-atlanta\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in Atlanta consistently rave about Wagging Tails Doggie Daycare & Boarding. This facility features spacious exercise zones, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Atlanta\",\"addressRegion\":\"GA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}25:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2d\"}}]\n2e:T5bd,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I walk my dog indoors in Atlanta?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Not yet in our verified directory for Atlanta. If you know a great indoor option, you can submit it and we’ll review it for inclusion.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in the City of Atlanta?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Atlanta strictly enforces leash laws in all public spaces. Dogs must be on a leash at all times unless they are within the fenced boundaries of a designated off-leash dog park. Owners must also maintain control of their pets and are legally required to remove any waste immediately.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed in Piedmont Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Piedmont Park is extremely dog-friendly. It features the Piedmont Park Dog Park, a premier off-leash area with separate enclosures for large and small breeds. Outside of this area, dogs are welcome on leashes throughout the park's many scenic paths and meadows.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the requirements for Atlanta dog parks?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Dogs must be at least four months old, current on rabies vaccinations, and wearing visible tags. Prong, pinch, or spiked collars are typically prohibited within the off-leash zones to ensure a safe play environment for all canine visitors.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Atlanta\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Atlanta\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park in Atlanta, GA\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Experience the urban energy of Atlanta, featuring the iconic Piedmont Park and a thriving community of dog-friendly businesses and green spaces.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Atlanta, Georgia, is a premier destination for dog owners who value a blend of urban excitement and lush green spaces. The city's pet culture is anchored by the iconic \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.piedmontpark.org\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Piedmont Park\"}],null,\", which provides a massive off-leash area and miles of scenic trails with skyline views. Neighborhoods like the Old Fourth Ward and Inman Park offer easy access to the \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.beltline.org\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Atlanta BeltLine\"}],null,\", a multi-use trail perfect for leashed exploration and socialization. Many residents visit our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/about\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"about page\"}],null,\" to learn more about our commitment to finding high-quality, professionally managed environments that complement the city's active and diverse pet lifestyle.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Maintaining a safe and welcoming environment is a top priority for the Atlanta community, supported by strict leash laws and ordinances that require immediate waste removal. These regulations ensure that the city's many shared spaces, from the vibrant Centennial Olympic Park to local neighborhood hubs, remain pristine for everyone. The city's active spirit leads many owners to seek out specialized \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"training facilities\"}],null,\" to maintain their dogs' social skills for outings in the many dog-friendly districts. During the humid summer months, there is high demand for \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/how-it-works\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"how it works\"}],null,\" for indoor play, providing a climate-controlled reprieve for year-round exercise and socialization.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"classNam