s\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Atlanta\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park in Atlanta, GA\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Experience the urban energy of Atlanta, featuring the iconic Piedmont Park and a thriving community of dog-friendly businesses and green spaces.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Atlanta, Georgia, is a premier destination for dog owners who value a blend of urban excitement and lush green spaces. The city's pet culture is anchored by the iconic \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.piedmontpark.org\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Piedmont Park\"}],null,\", which provides a massive off-leash area and miles of scenic trails with skyline views. Neighborhoods like the Old Fourth Ward and Inman Park offer easy access to the \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.beltline.org\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Atlanta BeltLine\"}],null,\", a multi-use trail perfect for leashed exploration and socialization. Many residents visit our \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/about\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"about page\"}],null,\" to learn more about our commitment to finding high-quality, professionally managed environments that complement the city's active and diverse pet lifestyle.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Maintaining a safe and welcoming environment is a top priority for the Atlanta community, supported by strict leash laws and ordinances that require immediate waste removal. These regulations ensure that the city's many shared spaces, from the vibrant Centennial Olympic Park to local neighborhood hubs, remain pristine for everyone. The city's active spirit leads many owners to seek out specialized \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"training facilities\"}],null,\" to maintain their dogs' social skills for outings in the many dog-friendly districts. During the humid summer months, there is high demand for \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/how-it-works\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"how it works\"}],null,\" for indoor play, providing a climate-controlled reprieve for year-round exercise and socialization.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[\"$L12\",\"$L13\"]}]]}],\"$L14\"]}]}],\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$undefined\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\",\"